      <PointerOffset>37508</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_014_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あっ……&lt;DIO&gt;！
ヒジに擦り傷が！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ah... &lt;DIO&gt;! You’ve got a scrape on your elbow!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <StructId>1</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>24</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37760</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_014_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ツバつけときゃ治るって。
死なない死なない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Just spit on it, it’ll heal. You’re not gonna die.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <StructId>2</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38192</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_014_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>背中にも青アザできてる！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You’ve got a bruise on your back too!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <StructId>3</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>24</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38504</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_014_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>全然だいじょーぶ！　痛くねーし</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I’m totally fine! It doesn’t even hurt.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <StructId>4</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38948</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_014_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>痛くなくても、ばい菌が入ったラ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Even if it doesn’t hurt, bacteria could get in...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <StructId>5</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>24</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39368</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_014_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いつもエトに心配かけて。
落ち着いて行動しないからでしょ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You’re always making Ethos worry. It’s because you don’t act calmly.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <StructId>6</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39964</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_014_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、&lt;MEL&gt;、ヒザから血が出てるぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh, &lt;MEL&gt;, your knee is bleeding.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <StructId>7</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40256</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_014_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え……ほ、ほんとだ……
ど、どうしよう！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Eh... R-Really... What should we do?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <StructId>8</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40912</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_014_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>さっき魔物と戦ってこけた時のだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It’s from when I fought the monster and fell earlier.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <StructId>9</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41080</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_014_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>早くばんそうこう！
あ、その前に消毒しなきゃ……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Quick, the band-aid! Ah, but first, I need to disinfect it...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <StructId>10</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>24</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41740</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_014_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うぅ……痛ぃよ……エト〜</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ugh... It hurts... Ethos~</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <StructId>11</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42776</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_014_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……落ち着けよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Calm down.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>12</Id>
